Net-CIMD version 0.01
=====================

Net::CIMD implement Computer Interface to Message Distribution, which's a protocol used to exchange messages betweeb Service Providers and SMS Centers.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module is pure perl implementation, and requires no other modules or libraries.

